Fig. 6E
). Parameres symmetrical, almost as long as maximum width, mesal margin rounded, setae emanating from distal 1/3 of dorsal surface. Proctiger almost as long as width at base. Pygophore with elongate setae sparsely distributed over most of surface, with thick brush of elongate setae on posterior margin (
Fig. 6F
